 href=\"https://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=Lg84ZazuoAMv777FGbMFAaooFDKVeMyzaQj0gYzwHSI%3D&h=bfba79d8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n908 美領<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/hk908ch\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhk908ch&d=Lg84ZazuoAMv777FGbMFAaooFDKVeMyzaQj0gYzwHSI%3D&h=fd15bc09\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hk908ch</a><br />\n<br />\n我係機場保安7號嗰日有少少野想同大家講<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1543735\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1543735</a><br />\n<br />\n點解話機場係春袋？<br />\n香港從來未試過咁樣未開始已經高調搜查交通工具<br />\n點解今次要提早搜查，唔等大家入到機場先搞？因為只要大家緊記今日策略，緊記自己市民/旅客，警察係冇辦法唔放行，大家入到機場混入遊客當中警察就冇辦法<br />\n唔敢搭巴士入機場嘅可以先去東涌或者香港站<br />\n未到一點機場入口已經排緊隊，已經入左機場嘅手足等緊大家<br />\n<br />\n目前仲可以去機場既方法<br />\n巴士路線 : 任何E車到達青馬收費廣場再轉A車  <br />\n黨鐵 : 東涌站 機場shuttle<br />\n機場快線：香港站<br />\n<br />\n或者任何你諗到既方法進入機場<br />\n<br />\n記住我地今日既目標  <br />\n不口號 不blackbloc <br />\n安安靜靜做番一個遊客旅行會做既事<br />\n<br />\n帶多幾支水以防中暑呀<br />\n<br />\n期待各位既奧斯卡演技"},{"pid":"9958c7cbf99e0295d14773484a25feb3d5ba0fe8","tid":1548511,"uid":167142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T04:42:30.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"35f2ec46fd7254cae6e46a7704b2b4ba885e38e4","tid":1548511,"uid":308225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T04:42:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">有備無患啊!</span>"},{"pid":"658a762fd85cb9a37b0bc7b4efa4e9ecbb396d35","tid":1548511,"uid":308225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T04:42:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ced5d803bff1b424b8bb7ccb01777e4cb8da934d","tid":1548511,"uid":308225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T04:43:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cc4120ab12fcf829e395ef591f6c0dc438631746","tid":1548511,"uid":308225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T04:43:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx